<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10124>
    dc:description "Figure 7. Cuatrecasanthus kingii: A Habit B Detail of adaxial surface of leaf C Cluster of heads D Single head containing one floret E Floret showing corolla lobes divided to base of limb, with thickened margins F Style G Achene with 8 - 10 ribs." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10124" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10126>
    dc:description "Figure 9. Cuatecasanthus lanceolatus: A Habit B Cluster of heads C Single head containing one floret D Floret showing corolla lobes divided to base of limb, with thickened margins and apical pubescence E Style F Achene with 8 - 10 ribs." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10126" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10118>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Cuatrecasanthus leaves: A Cuatrecasanthus lanceolatus showing projecting marginal tooth B Cuatrecasanthus kingii showing incurved tooth C Myceliform hairs on abaxial surface of leaf of Cuatrecasanthus giannasii." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10118" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10119>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Cuatrecasanthus leaf surfaces: A-B Cuatrecasanthus flexipappus. A Adaxial surface B Abaxial surface C-D Cuatrecasanthus giannasii C Adaxial surface, showing deeply insculpate veins D Abaxial surface." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10119" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10121>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Cuatrecasanthus leaf surfaces: A-B Cuatrecasanthus lanceolatus. A Adaxial surface B Abaxial surface C-D Cuatrecasanthus sandemanii C Adaxial surface D Abaxial surface." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10121" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

